# Implementation Plan - Cognitive Canvas v2.0 Initialization

# Goal Description
Initialize the codebase for the "Cognitive Canvas v2.0" including the FastAPI backend, React frontend with React Flow, and necessary configuration for Neo4j and Gemini.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This plan assumes a fresh start in the `nextstep-ver1` directory.
> Ensure Neo4j instance is running and credentials will be available in `.env`.
> Ensure Gemini API Key will be available in `.env`.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend
#### [NEW] [main.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver1/backend/main.py)
- Setup FastAPI app.
- Configure CORS.
- Define basic routes.

#### [NEW] [database.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver1/backend/database.py)
- Neo4j driver connection logic.

#### [NEW] [models.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver1/backend/models.py)
- Pydantic models for Node, Edge, and Graph responses.

#### [NEW] [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver1/backend/requirements.txt)
- `fastapi`, `uvicorn`, `neo4j`, `langgraph`, `google-generativeai`.

### Frontend
#### [NEW] [package.json](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver1/frontend/package.json)
- React, React Flow, Axios.

#### [NEW] [vite.config.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver1/frontend/vite.config.js)
